MAGBAND			26-Jan-89	(Pedro Gigoux)

This directory contains the code of the magband and magavg tasks. The first
one computes the magnitudes of one-dimensional spectra for a set of bandpasses,
and the second one averages the output of the first one to get statistics.
The files contained here are:

magavg.com		magavg common

mkpkg			mkpkg file

t_magavg.x		magavg procedures

t_magband.x		magband procedures
